## Features
- Random Company Generator
- Supply Chain Crisis Simulation
- War Room Decision Making
- Supplier Negotiation Rounds
- CEO Leadership Assessment
- AI Supply Chain Investments
- Executive Business Dashboard
- Replay Simulation

